# AI 2026: Enterprise RAG Observability — Traces, Evals, and Safety Telemetry

Production RAG systems demand deep visibility: retrieval quality, grounding, safety, and costs per task.

What to instrument:

- Retrieval traces with document IDs and confidence
- Grounding checks with citation density targets (> 0.9)
- Safety filters and redaction outcomes per hop
- Cost, latency, and cache performance per request

Operational targets: p95 latency < 250ms for interactive flows, citation density > 0.9, audit‑ready evidence for approvals.

