Operating RAG in production requires visibility into retrieval quality, grounding, and failure modes. This post offers a practical telemetry model and governance hooks.

## Telemetry

- Retrieval hits, reranker scores, citation density
- Groundedness checks and constraint violations

## Governance

- Policy-as-code guardrails at deploy and runtime
- Audit-ready traces and incident workflows

